OL,3,CJoey Barton guilty of 'grossly
OL,4,Coffensive' social media posts
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Tim
OL,7,FScott was at Liverpool Crown Court for
OL,8,Fthe verdicts
OL,10,FFormer footballer Joey Barton has been
OL,11,Ffound guilty of sending "grossly
OL,12,Foffensive" messages on social media
OL,13,Fabout broadcaster Jeremy Vine and TV
OL,14,Ffootball pundits Lucy Ward and Eni
OL,15,FAluko.
OL,17,FBarton, 43, was found to have "crossed
OL,18,Fthe line between free speech and a
OL,19,Fcrime" on six charges with posts he
OL,20,Fmade on social media platform X.
