OL,3,CJoey Barton guilty of 'grossly
OL,4,Coffensive' social media posts
OL,6,FA jury at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,7,Fcleared him of six other counts that
OL,8,Fhe sent a grossly offensive electronic
OL,9,Fcommunication with intent to cause
OL,10,Fdistress or anxiety between January
OL,11,Fand March 2024.
OL,13,FFollowing a televised FA Cup tie in
OL,14,FJanuary 2024 between Crystal Palace
OL,15,Fand Everton, Barton likened Ward and
OL,16,FAluko in a post on X to the "Fred and
OL,17,FRose West of football commentary".
OL,19,FHe then went on to superimpose the
OL,20,Ffaces of the two women on to a
OL,21,Fphotograph of the serial murderers.
