OL,6,FBarton also tweeted Aluko was in the
OL,7,F"Joseph Stalin/Pol Pot category" as
OL,8,Fthat she had "murdered hundreds of
OL,9,Fthousands, if not millions, of
OL,10,Ffootball fans' ears".
OL,12,FJurors found him not guilty on the
OL,13,FStalin/Pol Pot comparison, and also
OL,14,Fthe commentary analogy with the Wests,
OL,15,Fbut did rule the superimposed image
OL,16,Fwas grossly offensive.
