OL,6,FBarton was also found guilty of other
OL,7,Ftweets in relation to Vine in which he
OL,8,Freferred to him as "bike nonce" and
OL,9,Fsaid: "If you see this fella by a
OL,10,Fprimary school call 999," and "Beware
OL,11,FMan with Camera on his helmets
OL,12,Fcruising past primary schools. Call
OL,13,Fthe Cops if spotted".
OL,15,FHe was cleared of guilt over three
OL,16,Fremaining tweets referring to Vine.
OL,18,FBarton was bailed ahead of sentencing
