OL,6,FThe Honorary Recorder of Liverpool,
OL,7,FAndrew Menary KC, noted the defendant
OL,8,Fwas wearing a Union Jack patterned
OL,9,Fscarf as the verdicts were returned.
OL,11,FHe told the court: "He has chosen to
OL,12,Fadorn himself with a particular flag
OL,13,Fwhich I suppose is a stunt to make a
OL,14,Fpoint. He will not be permitted to do
OL,15,Fthat on the sentencing date."
