OL,6,FBarton said he had no intention of
OL,7,Fimplying Vine was a paedophile.
OL,9,FIn his closing speech to the jury of
OL,10,Fseven men and five women, prosecutor
OL,11,FPeter Wright KC said Barton had
OL,12,Fcrossed the line "by some considerable
OL,13,Fmargin" beyond what is tolerable in
OL,14,Fsociety.
OL,16,FHe said: "Mr Barton is not the victim
OL,17,Fhere.
OL,19,F"He is not the free speech crusader
OL,20,Fthat he would like to paint himself to
OL,21,Fbe.
