OL,6,F"He is not some martyr to be
OL,7,Fsacrificed on the altar of political
OL,8,Fcorrectness.
OL,10,F"He is just simply an undiluted,
OL,11,Funapologetic bully.
OL,13,F"A little bully who takes pleasure
OL,14,Fsitting there with his phone in his
OL,15,Fhand and then posting these slurs."
OL,17,FMr Wright said Ward, Aluko and Vine
OL,18,Fwere the "collateral damage of his
