OL,6,F"The criminal law is not there to
OL,7,Fpunish bad manners, sharp humour, or
OL,8,Funpopular opinions.
OL,10,F"The law only intervenes when the
OL,11,Fcontent is of such an extreme,
OL,12,Fdegrading or dehumanising character
OL,13,Fthat society as a whole would say `
OL,14,F'that goes too far, that crosses the
OL,15,Fline of what we can tolerate'."
